## ğŸ“Š Viewing Results

### Interactive Dashboards

After running the system, open these files in your browser:

- `outputs/dashboard.html` - Comprehensive multi-panel dashboard
- `outputs/route_map.html` - Delivery route visualization
- `outputs/timeline.html` - Performance over multiple cycles (if applicable)

### JSON Results

Detailed results are saved as JSON files:

- `outputs/cycle_1_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.json`

These contain complete data including:
- Settlement zone information
- Priority assessments
- Resource allocations
- Delivery routes and schedules
- Actual outcomes and analysis
- Performance metrics

